➡grass upper 3x60
➡side kick 3x20 each ➡donkey kick 3x20 ➡kick back 3x20 ➡side kick + leg raise 3x15
.

node.text:
HIGH PROTEIN COOKIE DOUGH DIP 

This recipe has taken off on TikTok & for good reason!I have gotten so many messages from those of you who’ve tried it & it’s been a hit in your lives too! Recipe below in case you missed it! SAVE THIS REEL TO MAKE IT LATER🤌
 
1 cup greek yogurt (or dairy free alternative of choice) 
1/2 cup nut butter of choice (I recommend cashew or peanut butter) 
2-3 tbsp maple syrup  
Pinch of sea salt 
1/4 tsp vanilla extract 
1/2 cup dark chocolate chips 
Optional: 1 batch of my protein cookie dough a few posts back for the topping! 
 
Mix all of the ingredients into a bowl & serve with fruit, rice cakes, crackers etc!  Store in the fridge & enjoy!✨ 
 
 by @laus_healthy_life 
 
#laushealthylife #highprotein #cookiedough

node.text: How does the band not break? 😅

Arms & Core 🔥🥵 Amazing workout that left me so sweaty and with a great arm pump. Lean back ‘slightly’ to engage your core with every lift. Keep your chest up and your back straight. Let’s get those strong arms! 💪
.
▪️3-4 sets, 12-20 reps each exercise 
▪️seated alternating static front raises (2 10lbs) 
▪️kneeling DB overhead extension (10lbs)
▪️DB front raise with lean backs (10lbs)
▪️seated alternating shoulder press (2 10lbs)
▪️seated wide bicep curls (2 10lbs)
▪️Russian twists (10lbs)
.
.
.
.
Cc: @built.by.becky 
.
#leanmuscle #core #coreworkout #abs #abworkout #sixpack #shoulders #fitnessmotivation #workoutmotivation #workoutathome #exercise
